description:
In episode 1075, Jack and guest co-host Joelle Monique are joined by comedian and co-host of What's It Called? Dave Ross to discuss Cuba Is Nailing Covid Response Despite Continual Starvation By US Embargo, Rihanna and ASAP Rocky Are Expecting The Most Well Dressed Baby In Human History and more!

  1. Cuba Is Nailing Covid Response Despite Continual Starvation By US Embargo
  2. Cuba’s vaccine success story sails past mark set by rich world’s Covid efforts
  3. Despite U.S. Embargo, Cuba Aims to Share Homegrown Vaccine with Global South
  4. The ‘Happy Planet Index’ Ranks Venezuela, Albania, and Cuba Far Higher than the United States


LISTEN: Heart Storm (with NAO) by serpentwithfeet
